--------------------

Annie: Before we finalize everything, let's write one more specific suggestion for my roommate — something beyond just "use the checklists." Something practical she can actually do, knowing that she's juggling this with her own coursework. You can look at the AI suggestions for ideas, but put it in your own words. [face=smile]

::fba3_revision_email [display=target:psych_sba_sidebar4auto label="Write One More Suggestion"]

